{
  "texts": [
    "train text is not included during pretraining to eliminate the overlap of pretraining data between acc extra and acc test.",
    "This choice was made in an effort to widen any gap between them.",
    "train contains m = 50 or m = 100 observations.",
    "m = 50 is inspired by the RAFT benchmark.",
    "m = 100 stretches the intention of \"few\" in few-shot learning, but was tested in an attempt to make lower-variance comparisons."
  ]
}